snippet: LEAD: Buck Helm, the longshoreman who survived for 90 hours in the wreckage of a freeway that collapsed in the California earthquake last month, died Saturday night. He became 58 years old on Nov. 10....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: Buck Helm, the longshoreman who survived for 90 hours in the wreckage of a freeway that collapsed in the California earthquake last month, died Saturday night. He became 58 years old on Nov. 10.

headline.main: Man Who Lived 90 Hours In Quake Rubble Is Dead
